javax.faces.component.StateHolder
public class HtmlPanelGrid
extends javax.faces.component.html.HtmlPanelGrid

This is an extension of javax.faces.component.html.HtmlPanelGrid, which provides some additional behavior to this component such as:

  • changes the component's rendered state based on the authentication
  • adds effects to the component
